original_title: Cracker and Camper Van Beethoven: First Annual Camp Out Live
overview: Documentary - On September 9 & 10, 2005, the bands Camper Van Beethoven and Cracker hosted the first Camp Out. Led by singer David Lowery, the bands celebrated two decades of work by coordinating special concerts with lineups featuring the original members. -  Cracker, Johnny Hickman, Victor Krummenacher
title: Cracker and Camper Van Beethoven: First Annual Camp Out Live
